WEBVTT

00:11.640 --> 00:18.320
[2012]

00:11.800 --> 00:12.430
Qi Yan.

00:15.430 --> 00:17.760
You've caused serious trouble this time.

00:18.390 --> 00:19.030
Really?

00:19.710 --> 00:21.070
You killed a cop!

00:22.350 --> 00:25.210
Dad's factory
in the mountains was also taken down.

00:25.640 --> 00:26.600
He is furious.

00:27.710 --> 00:28.960
Now Dad suspects

00:30.990 --> 00:33.190
that the factory's location was leaked

00:34.620 --> 00:37.020
because you couldn't keep your mouth shut.

00:37.490 --> 00:38.130
What?

00:40.620 --> 00:42.750
Does Wen Hongsheng want to silence me?

00:43.030 --> 00:44.310
Why would you think that?

00:44.310 --> 00:45.880
How could I not think that?

00:48.670 --> 00:50.240
He's always disliked me.

00:51.200 --> 00:52.470
Ever since you brought me back

00:52.470 --> 00:54.030
to your so-called home,

00:55.710 --> 00:57.240
he's wanted to get rid of me.

00:59.630 --> 01:00.270
Qi Yan,

01:03.400 --> 01:05.530
I'm only going to ask you one question.

01:06.160 --> 01:07.160
Does it really...

01:09.190 --> 01:10.720
have nothing to do with you?

01:13.380 --> 01:14.610
You don't believe me?

01:18.030 --> 01:19.890
Even you don't believe me, do you?

01:27.580 --> 01:28.730
No one believes me.

01:30.500 --> 01:32.890
I only wanted to chat with Ming!

01:33.340 --> 01:35.780
How was I supposed to know
the cops would show up?

01:35.780 --> 01:37.509
Did I want to get caught by them?

01:37.810 --> 01:39.580
Did I want to die?

01:43.580 --> 01:44.220
It's fine.

01:45.360 --> 01:47.340
Ming will take the fall for everything.

01:47.340 --> 01:48.070
Don't worry.

01:49.280 --> 01:50.740
I can never be in the light.

01:53.520 --> 01:55.450
I can never live in broad daylight.

01:58.720 --> 02:00.250
I want to be like you,

02:01.830 --> 02:03.090
standing in the light.

02:07.160 --> 02:08.280
I'm scared.

02:10.090 --> 02:11.810
I'm really scared.

02:32.690 --> 02:33.340
I'm sorry,

02:34.850 --> 02:35.500
Qi Yan.

02:38.300 --> 02:39.940
Maybe this is just my fate.

02:41.300 --> 02:43.570
The cops have blocked every way out now.

02:44.780 --> 02:45.900
I need a place

02:47.340 --> 02:48.060
to hide.

02:49.220 --> 02:50.880
Just like when we were kids...

02:56.220 --> 02:57.780
in Mom's closet.

03:24.220 --> 03:25.500
I know a place.

03:29.060 --> 03:30.500
Dad has a warehouse here.

03:31.500 --> 03:33.300
You can hide in there for a while.

03:33.740 --> 03:34.600
It's very safe.

03:35.250 --> 03:35.970
Very safe.

05:05.690 --> 05:11.430
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

05:11.790 --> 05:14.090
[Episode 26]

06:26.500 --> 06:27.420
Officer Zhou,

06:29.210 --> 06:30.210
nice to meet you.

06:31.940 --> 06:34.690
And it's an honor to have you
listen to me play the piano.

06:34.690 --> 06:35.550
How do you feel?

06:37.100 --> 06:39.100
I once planned to kill you right away

06:39.659 --> 06:41.010
and gouge out your eyes

06:41.100 --> 06:42.560
to give to Jiang Hansheng.

06:44.010 --> 06:46.670
But you look really beautiful
in this red dress.

06:48.740 --> 06:49.810
So gorgeous.

06:51.500 --> 06:52.210
So,

06:53.810 --> 06:54.810
I changed my mind.

06:57.570 --> 06:58.659
A beautiful woman

07:00.600 --> 07:02.830
should die a beautiful death.

07:04.330 --> 07:05.330
I personally don't like

07:05.330 --> 07:06.660
inartistic behaviors.

07:07.450 --> 07:08.450
So, Officer Zhou,

07:09.450 --> 07:11.380
I'd like to apologize to you first.

07:12.000 --> 07:13.450
Were it not for Jiang Hansheng,

07:13.450 --> 07:14.980
our meeting would have been

07:19.140 --> 07:20.430
much more elegant.

07:24.870 --> 07:26.600
You are just like your husband.

07:27.690 --> 07:29.220
When I express my goodwill,

07:30.190 --> 07:31.240
you both like...

07:33.850 --> 07:35.310
You like to remain silent.

07:40.850 --> 07:42.159
Do you feel them?

07:43.250 --> 07:46.170
Do you feel
the cartilage and muscles here?

07:47.830 --> 07:49.190
They are very fragile,

07:50.409 --> 07:51.140
aren't they?

07:52.770 --> 07:53.980
So, Officer Zhou,

07:55.450 --> 07:56.890
say something.

07:58.520 --> 08:00.320
It's good for you.

08:05.010 --> 08:08.010
Did you do the same thing
to Zhao Xiaoyu and the others?

08:16.570 --> 08:18.500
So this is the first thing you said.

08:20.610 --> 08:21.740
How disappointing.

08:25.080 --> 08:26.610
They were all failed works.

08:28.620 --> 08:30.890
So they were not qualified to come here.

08:32.610 --> 08:34.270
There isn't anything special

08:34.340 --> 08:35.740
about your concert hall.

08:37.970 --> 08:38.610
Is that so?

08:48.780 --> 08:50.980
Do you know who this place was set up for?

08:53.490 --> 08:54.490
My elder brother.

08:56.420 --> 08:57.850
The one who chose
to surrender 5 years ago,

08:57.850 --> 08:59.140
but was still shot

08:59.140 --> 09:00.810
and killed by your husband.

09:01.490 --> 09:03.490
My twin brother.

09:08.610 --> 09:09.690
So, Officer Zhou,

09:10.780 --> 09:12.570
do you know why

09:12.570 --> 09:14.610
I brought you here now?

09:27.870 --> 09:28.460
Chief Tan.

09:28.460 --> 09:29.060
Bai Yang,

09:29.090 --> 09:30.180
I've applied for this case

09:30.180 --> 09:31.860
and the attack on Director Wang Pengze

09:31.860 --> 09:34.020
to be merged
into the 8/17 Case's task force.

09:34.020 --> 09:35.440
We will participate directly
in the investigation.

09:35.440 --> 09:37.390
The documents for the joint task force
will be issued soon.

09:37.390 --> 09:38.570
You should proceed accordingly.

09:38.570 --> 09:39.540
Okay, understood.

09:39.540 --> 09:41.200
How is Professor Jiang doing?

09:43.980 --> 09:45.950
Can't tell right now.

09:45.970 --> 09:47.430
But he's still quite calm.

09:48.020 --> 09:49.470
Okay, got it.

09:52.730 --> 09:53.490
Chief Tan,

09:53.530 --> 09:55.390
Zhou Jin's car accident report is out.

09:55.390 --> 09:56.490
I'll send you a copy.

09:56.490 --> 09:57.020
Okay.

10:03.090 --> 10:04.070
Wait, Officer Jiang.

10:04.070 --> 10:05.210
You haven't been reinstated yet.

10:05.210 --> 10:05.660
You can't participate.

10:05.660 --> 10:07.060
Where is Jiang Hansheng?

10:09.020 --> 10:09.590
Well...

10:09.670 --> 10:10.420
Officer Jiang.

10:10.420 --> 10:11.680
Officer Jiang, you...

10:12.900 --> 10:15.050
As an insider, I have the right
to assist in the investigation.

10:15.050 --> 10:16.170
It's dated today.

10:34.870 --> 10:36.470
You have one chance to speak.

10:37.730 --> 10:38.730
Professor Jiang!

10:39.220 --> 10:40.080
Officer Jiang.

10:40.470 --> 10:41.190
Zhou Jin's

10:41.470 --> 10:43.670
accident investigation report is out.

10:44.730 --> 10:45.330
Go ahead.

10:46.040 --> 10:47.660
Chief Zhan from the Information Department

10:47.660 --> 10:49.380
of the Provincial Bureau is awake
at the hospital.

10:49.380 --> 10:50.110
Zhan Wei?

10:50.740 --> 10:51.330
Yes.

10:51.960 --> 10:54.240
He said his child
just had a one-month party.

10:54.240 --> 10:55.840
Zhou Jin told him
that she was in Jingzhou on business

10:55.840 --> 10:57.260
and wanted to visit the child by the way.

10:57.260 --> 10:59.260
So he drove to pick Zhou Jin up today.

10:59.480 --> 11:01.060
On the way, he suddenly found
that the brakes failed.

11:01.060 --> 11:01.960
After losing control of the steering,

11:01.960 --> 11:03.350
he crashed
right into the roadside barrier.

11:03.350 --> 11:05.180
He jumped out of the car
in advance to survive.

11:05.180 --> 11:06.020
Because he fell hard,

11:06.020 --> 11:07.420
he passed out after that.

11:07.610 --> 11:08.610
But he is very sure

11:08.780 --> 11:09.570
that before he fainted,

11:09.570 --> 11:10.940
he saw a black sedan

11:10.940 --> 11:11.970
take Zhou Jin away.

11:11.970 --> 11:13.870
The Provincial Bureau
has verified the statement.

11:13.870 --> 11:15.570
It basically matches the scene.

11:15.570 --> 11:16.970
The traffic accident department said

11:16.970 --> 11:18.730
the brake line was tampered with.

11:18.730 --> 11:19.850
But as for who did it,

11:19.850 --> 11:21.140
Zhan Wei has no clue, either.

11:21.140 --> 11:22.450
We've got someone on guard
at the hospital now.

11:22.450 --> 11:24.200
Just keep an eye on him normally.

11:24.200 --> 11:26.060
You think Zhan Wei is suspicious?

11:30.440 --> 11:31.420
Where are you going?

11:31.420 --> 11:32.350
To the hospital.

11:41.730 --> 11:42.460
This clock is

11:43.070 --> 11:44.070
going backwards.

11:46.790 --> 11:48.330
He only gave us 4 hours.

11:54.990 --> 11:55.990
Professor Jiang.

11:56.680 --> 11:57.290
Wan,

11:57.450 --> 11:58.350
it's in Room 2110.

11:58.350 --> 11:59.090
We're going to find someone.

11:59.090 --> 11:59.490
Okay.

11:59.510 --> 12:00.040
Go ahead.

12:13.200 --> 12:14.800
Do you need me to do anything?

12:25.560 --> 12:26.710
You stay in the car.

12:44.780 --> 12:46.710
How much do you know about Zhan Wei?

12:46.750 --> 12:48.810
How confident are you in your judgment?

12:48.810 --> 12:49.780
We don't have time right now

12:49.780 --> 12:52.510
to verify that the judgment is
completely right.

12:57.200 --> 12:58.120
I thought

12:58.150 --> 12:59.700
you were the gentle type.

13:02.970 --> 13:04.170
I hope you can help me.

13:05.610 --> 13:06.740
I'm not helping you.

13:13.330 --> 13:13.900
Alright,

13:14.210 --> 13:15.050
the wound's been treated.

13:15.050 --> 13:16.310
Stay here a bit longer.

13:36.790 --> 13:37.790
Professor Jiang,

13:38.380 --> 13:39.440
what are you doing?

13:39.940 --> 13:40.940
Where is Zhou Jin?

13:41.900 --> 13:43.500
How would I know where she is?

13:43.660 --> 13:44.850
I'm so sorry

13:45.620 --> 13:46.760
about what happened to Jin.

13:46.760 --> 13:47.780
But I really didn't know

13:47.780 --> 13:49.020
they would kidnap her.

13:49.020 --> 13:50.420
They tampered with my brakes.

13:50.420 --> 13:51.490
I almost died, too!

13:52.680 --> 13:54.610
You know I have no direct evidence,

13:55.400 --> 13:57.330
so you want to deny it to the end, right?

13:57.330 --> 13:58.780
I also see Jin as my younger sister.

13:58.780 --> 14:00.210
How could I possibly harm her?

14:00.210 --> 14:02.740
Your career's taken off
over the past 5 years.

14:03.080 --> 14:04.680
Zhou Chuan up there in heaven

14:05.250 --> 14:07.180
would also feel happy for you, huh?

14:11.600 --> 14:13.330
You think I'm here to scare you?

14:14.090 --> 14:15.700
You don't have much time left.

14:15.700 --> 14:17.230
Don't waste your time on me.

14:17.260 --> 14:19.720
I'm not here to talk
about evidence with you.

14:20.730 --> 14:22.930
I heard you value your family very much.

14:24.580 --> 14:25.510
What do you mean?

14:32.340 --> 14:34.250
Please, don't hurt my child!

14:34.510 --> 14:35.970
My child is still so little!

14:35.970 --> 14:36.780
Chief Zhan!

14:36.860 --> 14:38.540
Come back quickly, Chief Zhan!

14:38.540 --> 14:39.940
What are you trying to do?

14:40.140 --> 14:41.070
Jiang Hansheng,

14:41.210 --> 14:42.470
you're threatening me?

14:42.470 --> 14:43.860
Do you really dare to make a move?

14:43.860 --> 14:44.790
Look carefully.

14:45.230 --> 14:46.250
I'm not the one doing it.

14:46.250 --> 14:47.920
You are an accomplice, equally guilty!

14:47.920 --> 14:49.040
I just told him

14:49.550 --> 14:51.880
that it was you
who betrayed the police back then.

14:51.880 --> 14:54.180
It was you who leaked the information
about the undercover officers

14:54.180 --> 14:55.900
engaged in the 8/17 Case task force.

14:55.900 --> 14:56.380
I didn't!

14:56.380 --> 14:56.850
I never did that!

14:56.850 --> 14:58.250
Whether you did it or not,

14:59.040 --> 15:00.170
would he believe it?

15:00.630 --> 15:01.180
He?

15:02.140 --> 15:02.900
Who is he?

15:03.490 --> 15:04.820
What right does he have?

15:10.800 --> 15:11.900
I am Jiang Cheng.

15:12.020 --> 15:14.180
Do you think I have the right?

15:15.220 --> 15:15.750
Jiang...

15:16.170 --> 15:16.900
Jiang Cheng.

15:18.060 --> 15:18.640
Jiang Cheng,

15:18.640 --> 15:19.380
listen to me.

15:20.610 --> 15:21.810
I really didn't do it.

15:22.020 --> 15:22.680
I really...

15:22.930 --> 15:24.790
We used to be good buddies, right?

15:24.940 --> 15:27.560
I can't believe you actually
stabbed me in the back.

15:27.560 --> 15:28.710
Not to mention that Yao Weihai

15:28.710 --> 15:30.760
and Meng Junfeng died such tragic deaths.

15:30.760 --> 15:32.330
Do you think I'll let go of the one

15:32.330 --> 15:34.460
who betrayed them behind their backs?

15:35.210 --> 15:35.740
Cheng...

15:36.060 --> 15:36.610
Cheng...

15:37.260 --> 15:38.060
Believe me,

15:38.060 --> 15:39.540
I... I really didn't do it.

15:39.610 --> 15:40.270
Believe me.

15:49.200 --> 15:50.960
My chips are pretty clear now.

15:51.870 --> 15:52.620
Your turn.

15:54.300 --> 15:54.660
I...

15:55.460 --> 15:57.460
don't know.

16:01.410 --> 16:02.490
Nanshan Manor.

16:03.090 --> 16:04.570
I only know the name of the place.

16:04.570 --> 16:05.950
It's called Nanshan Manor.

16:05.950 --> 16:07.270
Old Scorpion told me that.

16:07.270 --> 16:09.130
He asked me to meet Zhou Jin alone.

16:10.450 --> 16:11.780
Where is Nanshan Manor?

16:13.490 --> 16:14.220
I don't know.

16:14.900 --> 16:15.700
I've checked.

16:16.490 --> 16:18.420
There's no such place in Jingzhou.

16:22.260 --> 16:23.060
Zhan Wei!

16:25.210 --> 16:25.900
Zhan Wei!

16:25.900 --> 16:26.830
What's going on?

16:27.140 --> 16:28.140
Professor Jiang!

16:28.490 --> 16:29.970
You put the pocket watch

16:31.420 --> 16:32.590
by Zhou Chuan's tomb, didn't you?

16:32.590 --> 16:33.650
I'll go get the key!

16:34.380 --> 16:35.020
Excuse me, excuse me.

16:35.020 --> 16:35.570
Zhan Wei!

16:37.720 --> 16:38.430
Hurry!

16:38.450 --> 16:38.930
Coming!

16:41.730 --> 16:42.730
Professor Jiang!

16:43.460 --> 16:44.460
Professor Jiang!

16:44.610 --> 16:45.610
Professor Jiang,

16:45.730 --> 16:46.440
calm down.

16:46.470 --> 16:48.000
Calm down. Don't go too far.

16:48.200 --> 16:48.870
Who are you?

16:48.970 --> 16:50.430
What were you trying to do?

16:50.630 --> 16:51.960
I'm Zhou Jin's husband.

16:52.280 --> 16:53.280
Professor Jiang!

16:53.490 --> 16:54.570
What's going on?

16:58.610 --> 16:59.540
What happened?

17:00.970 --> 17:03.780
There was a misunderstanding
between Professor Jiang and me,

17:03.780 --> 17:05.420
but it's over now.

17:14.490 --> 17:15.220
Got nothing?

17:16.530 --> 17:17.250
Not sure yet.

17:17.250 --> 17:18.310
What have you done?

17:18.940 --> 17:19.420
Well,

17:20.010 --> 17:21.849
the task force
has already sent police to search.

17:21.849 --> 17:24.010
The tech department is also
checking the surveillance along the way.

17:24.010 --> 17:25.940
Maybe they'll have some good news.

17:25.980 --> 17:27.640
Did you find Zhou Jin's phone?

17:27.690 --> 17:29.120
We found it at the crash scene,

17:29.120 --> 17:30.380
but it's been smashed to pieces.

17:30.380 --> 17:32.710
It will take some time
to recover the data.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.050
No!

17:43.800 --> 17:45.150
Lu Xin!

18:04.630 --> 18:06.030
Is that Professor Jiang?

18:06.720 --> 18:07.760
I-It's me.

18:08.900 --> 18:10.010
I am Qi Zhen.

18:12.890 --> 18:14.890
I have already arrived in Jingzhou.

18:18.800 --> 18:19.710
Last time,

18:20.190 --> 18:22.250
you and Officer Zhou came to my house.

18:22.770 --> 18:24.660
Sorry, because

18:25.120 --> 18:27.140
I was not
in a good state of mind back then,

18:27.140 --> 18:28.250
I kicked you out.

18:29.290 --> 18:30.420
It was because

18:31.050 --> 18:32.340
I was terrified.

18:33.450 --> 18:34.010
I...

18:34.730 --> 18:35.970
I was very scared...

18:37.990 --> 18:39.800
that Wen Hongsheng would come to hurt me

18:39.800 --> 18:41.110
and hurt Jian Liang.

18:42.380 --> 18:43.010
So,

18:43.600 --> 18:44.320
I'm sorry.

18:46.800 --> 18:48.120
Jian Liang told me.

18:48.450 --> 18:49.140
He said

18:49.730 --> 18:51.530
if you cannot face your past,

18:52.360 --> 18:53.520
there is no way

18:54.370 --> 18:56.020
for you to start a new life.

18:58.730 --> 19:01.140
I am willing to tell you
everything I know.

19:02.290 --> 19:04.150
Who did you say you were afraid of?

19:04.590 --> 19:05.450
Wen Hongsheng?

19:06.140 --> 19:07.540
How do you spell the name?

19:09.020 --> 19:11.060
"W-e-n" as in news,

19:12.050 --> 19:13.420
"H-o-n-g" as in wild goose,

19:13.420 --> 19:15.020
and "s-h-e-n-g" as in grand.

19:15.210 --> 19:17.070
Wen Hongsheng is Qi Yan's father?

19:19.060 --> 19:19.610
Yes.

19:20.940 --> 19:21.620
He is.

19:23.420 --> 19:24.970
I was 17

19:24.970 --> 19:26.580
when I met Wen Hongsheng.

19:27.000 --> 19:27.770
At that time,

19:28.140 --> 19:29.380
I hadn't finished high school

19:29.380 --> 19:30.510
and had dropped out.

19:30.900 --> 19:33.160
I worked in a towel factory
during the day

19:33.330 --> 19:33.960
and had

19:34.530 --> 19:37.290
a part-time job
selling soda in a pool hall at night

19:37.290 --> 19:38.350
to make more money.

19:40.620 --> 19:41.620
Give me 2 sodas!

19:41.900 --> 19:42.490
Coming.

19:47.660 --> 19:48.790
Here are your sodas.

19:52.940 --> 19:54.180
I can hardly remember

19:54.180 --> 19:56.290
what happened during that time now.

19:56.620 --> 19:59.250
I just remember
that after I got with Wen Hongsheng,

19:59.250 --> 20:00.580
he treated me very badly

20:01.290 --> 20:02.580
and often hit me.

20:03.620 --> 20:05.750
He wasn't doing legitimate business.

20:06.920 --> 20:07.730
He only did

20:08.060 --> 20:09.820
shady business.

20:10.380 --> 20:12.000
On the surface, he was in foreign trade,

20:12.000 --> 20:13.300
selling medicinal herbs,

20:13.300 --> 20:14.100
but secretly,

20:14.370 --> 20:16.230
he did whatever made quick money.

20:17.940 --> 20:19.000
I wanted to escape,

20:20.250 --> 20:21.820
but every time I ran away,

20:22.350 --> 20:24.630
I only ended up being beaten severely.

20:24.660 --> 20:25.700
How dare you run!

20:27.420 --> 20:28.450
How dare you run!

20:32.370 --> 20:33.250
Later,

20:34.860 --> 20:36.390
I learned to behave myself.

20:37.940 --> 20:40.870
There was even a time
when I started to accept my fate.

20:41.100 --> 20:41.620
Until

20:42.860 --> 20:43.860
I got pregnant.

20:46.450 --> 20:47.820
At that time, Wen Hongsheng was

20:47.820 --> 20:49.080
carried away with joy.

20:50.420 --> 20:53.220
He told me that as long as I gave birth
to a son of his,

20:53.530 --> 20:54.290
he would renovate

20:54.290 --> 20:56.890
the large villa in the suburbs
and give it to me.

20:57.210 --> 20:59.810
And he'd pass
all the family business to my son.

21:00.380 --> 21:02.180
He thought it was a reward for me,

21:02.710 --> 21:03.970
a favor bestowed on me.

21:04.660 --> 21:05.720
But when I heard it,

21:06.940 --> 21:08.340
it chilled me to the bone.

21:10.420 --> 21:11.950
They were also my children.

21:12.520 --> 21:14.010
I'd never bear to see my child

21:14.010 --> 21:15.530
become someone like him.

22:01.490 --> 22:03.090
Where exactly is this place?

22:04.770 --> 22:05.380
Home.

22:06.010 --> 22:06.530
Home?

22:11.250 --> 22:13.250
It's only a home if there are people.

22:13.730 --> 22:15.020
Besides you, is there

22:16.100 --> 22:17.100
anyone else here?

22:19.310 --> 22:20.170
Anyone else...

22:23.040 --> 22:24.630
Other people...

22:33.900 --> 22:34.580
Home...

22:37.250 --> 22:39.860
It is indeed a very distant concept.

22:43.450 --> 22:44.910
It was after I got pregnant

22:45.270 --> 22:48.730
that Wen Hongsheng gradually stopped
watching me so closely.

22:49.140 --> 22:50.210
I took advantage of a chance

22:50.210 --> 22:51.620
to go out shopping

22:52.290 --> 22:54.090
and sneaked back to my hometown.

22:54.820 --> 22:56.250
With my cousin's help,

22:56.270 --> 22:56.940
I went

22:56.940 --> 22:58.870
to a small town where no one knew me.

22:59.660 --> 23:00.790
I started a new life.

23:02.430 --> 23:04.030
I worked in a garment factory

23:04.600 --> 23:05.730
and learned sewing.

23:06.380 --> 23:08.510
Then I gave birth to my children there.

23:09.740 --> 23:11.470
The elder one was named Qi Lang.

23:11.730 --> 23:13.530
The younger one was named Qi Yan.

23:13.890 --> 23:16.090
We lived peaceful lives for a few years.

23:16.860 --> 23:18.060
At the time, I thought

23:18.530 --> 23:21.040
that Wen Hongsheng was
no longer interested in me

23:21.040 --> 23:22.900
and wouldn't look for me anymore.

23:24.900 --> 23:25.970
But unexpectedly,

23:27.210 --> 23:29.210
he had been looking for me all along.

23:29.690 --> 23:30.620
When his underlings

23:30.620 --> 23:32.420
found the factory where I lived.

23:33.050 --> 23:36.180
Wen Hongsheng sent men
to catch me that day immediately.

23:36.420 --> 23:38.880
He became even more terrifying
than before.

23:39.760 --> 23:40.600
They had guns.

23:42.040 --> 23:44.040
His men all called him Old Scorpion.

23:46.320 --> 23:47.360
I could tell

23:49.300 --> 23:51.430
that there was nothing he dared not do.

23:58.120 --> 23:59.650
You've lost so much weight.

24:05.820 --> 24:06.820
I beg you.

24:08.690 --> 24:10.220
I don't want anything else.

24:10.420 --> 24:11.730
Please let me go.

24:13.380 --> 24:14.100
Zhen.

24:16.530 --> 24:18.790
You need to return what you stole from me.

24:20.020 --> 24:21.170
Where is my child?

24:25.180 --> 24:26.000
I aborted it.

24:31.950 --> 24:33.190
Where is

24:34.010 --> 24:35.100
my child?

24:36.360 --> 24:37.680
Didn't you get it?

24:39.190 --> 24:40.450
Right after I left you,

24:40.490 --> 24:41.880
I just aborted it!

24:42.840 --> 24:43.760
Wen Hongsheng,

24:44.500 --> 24:47.290
did you really think
I'd give birth to a child for you?

24:47.290 --> 24:49.140
Just hearing your breathing

24:49.490 --> 24:50.940
makes me sick!

24:55.380 --> 24:56.920
Go find my child.

25:03.050 --> 25:04.180
That was when I was 9.

25:07.050 --> 25:08.200
How I wish

25:12.010 --> 25:14.340
the one rushing out of that wardrobe was

25:17.900 --> 25:18.580
me,

25:21.820 --> 25:22.780
Qi Yan.

25:26.900 --> 25:28.160
Take good care of Mom.

25:28.190 --> 25:29.640
Wait for me to pick you up.

25:35.050 --> 25:36.380
Who told you to come out?

25:37.310 --> 25:40.040
When Wen Hongsheng was
about to start searching,

25:40.420 --> 25:41.340
Lang

25:43.100 --> 25:44.580
ran out by himself

25:45.100 --> 25:47.760
and said he was willing to go
with Wen Hongsheng.

25:49.140 --> 25:51.800
Wen Hongsheng didn't know
I gave birth to twins,

25:52.900 --> 25:54.360
so he didn't look for more.

25:55.290 --> 25:56.290
Take my son home.

25:57.860 --> 25:59.970
Lang was mature from a young age.

26:01.250 --> 26:04.420
He protected his younger brother

26:05.450 --> 26:06.770
and me.

26:07.900 --> 26:08.380
Qi Zhen,

26:09.810 --> 26:11.670
you abandoned Qi Yan, didn't you?

26:17.000 --> 26:17.690
Why?

26:23.080 --> 26:23.560
I...

26:24.380 --> 26:25.340
I had no choice.

26:29.050 --> 26:31.210
I also wanted to raise him properly.

26:34.010 --> 26:35.180
I once thought

26:35.720 --> 26:37.470
that keeping a child by my side was

26:37.470 --> 26:39.600
a blessing among all the misfortunes.

26:40.820 --> 26:42.250
But I only found out later

26:43.900 --> 26:46.830
that it was just the beginning
of another nightmare.

26:48.860 --> 26:50.100
The older Yan grew,

26:50.700 --> 26:53.100
the more he showed
Wen Hongsheng's traits.

26:53.660 --> 26:54.790
He was cold-blooded

26:55.530 --> 26:56.290
and cruel,

26:57.700 --> 26:59.260
and he dared to do anything.

27:01.190 --> 27:02.920
I couldn't teach him properly.

27:03.820 --> 27:05.100
After he entered puberty,

27:05.100 --> 27:07.100
everything just scared me to death.

27:08.140 --> 27:08.860
I knew

27:10.380 --> 27:12.580
he'd only do evil as long as he was alive.

27:12.660 --> 27:13.620
I once wanted

27:13.620 --> 27:15.380
to have him die with me.

27:16.770 --> 27:17.380
But...

27:18.770 --> 27:20.620
But I couldn't do it.

27:24.580 --> 27:26.990
I'm his mother, after all.

27:34.940 --> 27:37.600
Your elder brother's called
Zhou Chuan, right?

27:38.900 --> 27:40.250
He was a good man,

27:41.620 --> 27:42.180
right?

27:44.580 --> 27:46.180
I also have an elder brother,

27:47.530 --> 27:48.490
just like you.

27:49.820 --> 27:51.050
When we reunited,

27:52.660 --> 27:54.210
I was a wanted murderer,

27:55.490 --> 27:57.250
and he was a gentle

27:57.660 --> 27:58.820
family heir.

28:00.250 --> 28:02.180
My brother treated me really well.

28:02.380 --> 28:03.770
Even though we were worlds apart,

28:03.770 --> 28:05.420
in just one week,

28:05.620 --> 28:07.880
he found someone to take the blame for me,

28:09.050 --> 28:11.250
helped me escape the police's pursuit,

28:11.860 --> 28:13.720
and brought me back to the family.

28:13.940 --> 28:14.800
You don't know.

28:15.940 --> 28:16.730
When Wen Lang

28:17.900 --> 28:18.620
took me

28:20.380 --> 28:22.180
to see my biological father,

28:24.730 --> 28:26.100
my father was so happy,

28:28.730 --> 28:29.580
overjoyed,

28:30.900 --> 28:31.900
and so surprised.

28:32.620 --> 28:33.750
His name is Wen Lang?

28:36.100 --> 28:36.660
Yes.

28:37.210 --> 28:38.340
His name is Wen Lang.

28:42.720 --> 28:44.250
I feel really sorry for him.

28:44.970 --> 28:45.830
Compared to me,

28:46.420 --> 28:48.350
he was the one who deserved to live.

28:50.580 --> 28:51.770
Sometimes, family is

28:51.770 --> 28:53.630
such a contradictory existence.

28:54.620 --> 28:55.970
I once loved him,

28:57.340 --> 28:59.210
but because he made a wrong decision,

28:59.210 --> 29:00.740
I hate him more than anyone.

29:01.660 --> 29:03.190
I hate him for abandoning me

29:04.100 --> 29:05.490
and owning everything,

29:06.210 --> 29:07.490
while leaving me

29:08.100 --> 29:10.540
like a battered stray dog,

29:10.570 --> 29:11.700
rotting there,

29:12.340 --> 29:13.820
rotting in the gutter

29:14.010 --> 29:15.180
for a lifetime.

29:17.100 --> 29:18.690
Yet he's up there on the moral high ground

29:18.690 --> 29:20.100
of love and sacrifice,

29:20.880 --> 29:22.880
receiving everyone's respect,

29:23.660 --> 29:24.530
thoughts,

29:24.810 --> 29:25.840
remembrance,

29:26.530 --> 29:27.490
and love.

29:29.940 --> 29:32.860
He gave me what was rightfully mine,
like he was

29:33.180 --> 29:34.660
doing me a favor!

29:35.900 --> 29:36.820
Why?

29:37.940 --> 29:39.620
Why should I accept it?

29:41.180 --> 29:41.940
Why?

29:46.820 --> 29:47.730
We're twins.

29:49.900 --> 29:50.690
Why?

29:55.920 --> 30:03.020
[2012]

29:56.940 --> 29:57.380
Lang.

29:59.850 --> 30:01.370
I think I'm screwed.

30:03.130 --> 30:03.990
I have a feeling

30:04.700 --> 30:05.500
that soon,

30:05.530 --> 30:06.940
the police will find me

30:07.420 --> 30:08.530
and arrest me.

30:10.380 --> 30:10.770
Lang.

30:14.180 --> 30:15.110
I'm a bit scared.

30:18.340 --> 30:19.400
I'm really scared.

30:20.520 --> 30:22.580
Why did you mess with Jiang Hansheng?

30:24.090 --> 30:25.970
Because this guy is really bad.

30:27.530 --> 30:28.530
He's very bad!

30:29.620 --> 30:31.010
This bastard is

30:31.490 --> 30:32.690
like a bug,

30:32.710 --> 30:34.040
crawling into my brain.

30:34.340 --> 30:36.530
He knows everything I'm thinking!

30:36.970 --> 30:37.970
You know what?

30:38.380 --> 30:39.530
He lured me first,

30:40.140 --> 30:41.970
and then provoked me!

30:42.140 --> 30:44.050
He's using me, Lang!

30:46.140 --> 30:47.490
What should I do?

30:53.530 --> 30:55.490
How can I escape?

30:55.800 --> 30:56.630
Wen Lang,

30:57.170 --> 30:58.650
I'm so scared.

31:06.670 --> 31:08.130
I'll take the fall for you.

31:10.290 --> 31:11.020
It will work.

31:19.050 --> 31:20.180
I'm squeaky-clean.

31:21.010 --> 31:22.470
They won't find anything.

31:23.940 --> 31:25.070
I'll tell the police

31:25.940 --> 31:27.200
that you kidnapped me.

31:29.210 --> 31:30.820
On August 17th
and the couple of days following,

31:30.820 --> 31:32.370
I had solid alibis.

31:33.620 --> 31:35.750
I'll let the police take me away first,

31:35.940 --> 31:37.540
and I won't say a word to them.

31:38.100 --> 31:39.380
I'll buy you more time

31:39.380 --> 31:40.100
to escape.

31:42.730 --> 31:43.460
It will work.

31:45.100 --> 31:45.760
But, Qi Yan,

31:47.340 --> 31:48.400
listen carefully.

31:49.210 --> 31:50.610
I'll get you some fake IDs

31:51.900 --> 31:53.760
and have someone send you abroad.

31:55.900 --> 31:57.160
Remember this lesson.

31:58.580 --> 32:00.580
This is the last time I will help you.

32:01.490 --> 32:02.690
Don't ever come back.

32:05.100 --> 32:06.030
Thank you, Lang.

32:06.770 --> 32:07.650
Thank you.

32:13.970 --> 32:15.430
My brother was very smart,

32:17.320 --> 32:19.320
but sometimes he was pretty stupid.

32:20.530 --> 32:22.250
He gave me everything,

32:23.100 --> 32:25.210
standing in front of Jiang Hansheng
and volunteering to take the blame for me.

32:25.210 --> 32:27.470
It was his own choice. I didn't force him.

32:27.520 --> 32:29.380
I didn't force him to do anything.

32:30.010 --> 32:31.870
I accepted everything he gave me.

32:32.490 --> 32:33.940
I deserved it.

32:34.860 --> 32:35.450
Why

32:36.670 --> 32:37.910
should I feel guilty?

32:40.260 --> 32:40.980
Do you think

32:42.530 --> 32:43.700
I seek revenge

32:43.720 --> 32:45.830
on Jiang Hansheng out of guilt?

32:48.970 --> 32:51.180
Jiang Hansheng ruined my plan,

32:51.490 --> 32:52.490
so he must accept

32:52.490 --> 32:53.620
a little punishment.

32:53.620 --> 32:54.940
This is a game,

32:55.140 --> 32:57.000
and games must be played by rules.

32:59.010 --> 33:00.070
And one more thing.

33:01.860 --> 33:03.920
Jiang Hansheng has someone he loves,

33:06.540 --> 33:08.430
the only person

33:08.690 --> 33:10.220
he'll ever love in his life.

33:14.420 --> 33:16.340
And that person is you,

33:18.360 --> 33:19.160
Officer Zhou.

33:20.840 --> 33:21.840
I don't like it.

33:27.660 --> 33:29.120
You are absolutely right,

33:29.790 --> 33:30.350
Qi Yan.

33:31.340 --> 33:32.320
You really are

33:33.320 --> 33:34.010
a stray dog

33:34.030 --> 33:36.620
rotting in the gutter.

33:37.450 --> 33:38.530
You are sick.

33:40.580 --> 33:41.490
You are flawed.

33:42.800 --> 33:44.260
You are incapable of love.

33:52.860 --> 33:53.660
Officer Zhou,

33:54.620 --> 33:55.380
do you think

33:56.820 --> 33:58.100
you can irritate me

33:58.100 --> 33:59.770
with just a few words?

34:11.090 --> 34:12.000
Officer Zhou,

34:13.010 --> 34:15.130
I have a gift for you.

34:24.860 --> 34:25.780
The household registration was

34:25.780 --> 34:27.440
cancelled in September 2012.

34:28.610 --> 34:30.340
I'll look into his business inheritance,

34:30.340 --> 34:31.870
cemetery, and real estate.

34:40.420 --> 34:40.900
Qi Zhen.

34:42.380 --> 34:43.980
We don't have much time left.

34:44.130 --> 34:45.060
I'll just ask you

34:45.489 --> 34:46.690
a question directly.

34:50.300 --> 34:51.560
Okay, please go ahead.

34:52.010 --> 34:53.820
Have you seen Qi Yan since then?

34:57.300 --> 34:58.300
I saw him once.

34:58.700 --> 34:59.170
Where?

35:00.010 --> 35:00.900
In Huaiguang.

35:01.970 --> 35:03.900
I have no idea how he made it either.

35:04.530 --> 35:06.130
He found Jian Liang's house.

35:06.700 --> 35:08.450
Was it before the serial murder cases

35:08.450 --> 35:09.170
or after?

35:09.610 --> 35:10.220
After.

35:11.300 --> 35:12.300
During that time,

35:12.740 --> 35:14.600
the cases were causing an uproar.

35:15.340 --> 35:16.870
Jian Liang was also tied up.

35:17.740 --> 35:20.270
I was the one who opened the door
when Yan came.

35:20.800 --> 35:21.530
He brought me a newspaper

35:21.530 --> 35:23.610
reporting a murder case

35:24.610 --> 35:25.940
and didn't say a word.

35:28.170 --> 35:29.420
I knew he did it.

35:31.650 --> 35:32.690
I probably got

35:34.090 --> 35:35.750
too emotionally overwhelmed

35:36.220 --> 35:37.530
and passed out.

35:40.050 --> 35:41.260
When I woke up,

35:43.740 --> 35:44.870
he was already gone.

35:45.450 --> 35:46.740
On the day you met,

35:47.340 --> 35:48.740
was Chief Jian's uniform

35:48.780 --> 35:50.840
still hanging on the wall by the door?

35:51.170 --> 35:52.630
Yes, it was hanging there.

35:53.450 --> 35:54.490
Why do you ask?

35:56.940 --> 35:58.340
Based on previous cases,

35:58.900 --> 35:59.900
Qi Yan's hatred is

35:59.900 --> 36:01.900
projected onto two kinds of people.

36:02.130 --> 36:03.730
First, women in red dresses.

36:04.610 --> 36:06.070
Second, police officers.

36:09.940 --> 36:11.200
And one last question.

36:12.820 --> 36:13.860
"Nanshan Manor."

36:14.360 --> 36:15.650
Do you have any impression

36:15.650 --> 36:16.700
of this place?

36:26.700 --> 36:28.050
Nanshan Manor?

36:31.050 --> 36:31.860
Nanshan...

36:40.130 --> 36:41.730
I don't have any impression.

36:47.900 --> 36:50.460
The great show is starting, Officer Zhou.

36:50.700 --> 36:51.900
I'll return it to you.

36:52.340 --> 36:53.260
Watch closely.

36:55.070 --> 36:56.640
I still remember that day.

36:58.970 --> 36:59.900
I miss it so much.

37:01.450 --> 37:02.570
I'll return it to you.

37:02.570 --> 37:03.940
Yeah, get up and take it.

37:04.260 --> 37:05.610
See that pocket watch?

37:05.940 --> 37:06.600
Here you go.

37:23.170 --> 37:23.820
Mr. Yan,

37:24.530 --> 37:25.260
take it back.

37:51.380 --> 37:51.900
Come on,

37:52.740 --> 37:53.600
Officer Jiang.

37:54.860 --> 37:55.820
Let's talk about

37:58.050 --> 37:58.970
your girl.

38:01.490 --> 38:02.550
I didn't expect it.

38:03.220 --> 38:04.480
I really didn't expect

38:06.130 --> 38:07.970
that the tough Officer Jiang

38:10.340 --> 38:12.130
would be shaken

38:12.130 --> 38:13.490
by a little girl.

38:15.770 --> 38:17.690
You're afraid I'll kill her.

38:31.340 --> 38:32.140
Officer Zhou,

38:33.490 --> 38:34.940
do you still think

38:36.480 --> 38:38.880
Jiang Hansheng was innocent when he shot

38:41.620 --> 38:42.880
and killed my brother?

38:46.810 --> 38:48.470
He said he was going to kill me.

38:49.780 --> 38:51.040
He was going to kill me.

38:52.940 --> 38:54.170
Hang in there.

38:57.460 --> 38:59.780
It hurts just looking at it.

39:01.610 --> 39:02.410
Officer Zhou,

39:03.090 --> 39:04.050
see?

39:05.740 --> 39:07.740
Do you see it clearly, Officer Zhou?

39:12.220 --> 39:13.130
Officer Jiang,

39:14.530 --> 39:15.260
does it hurt?

39:16.010 --> 39:17.610
It hurts so much, doesn't it?

39:18.300 --> 39:19.030
Does it hurt?

39:21.130 --> 39:22.390
You just need to beg me,

39:22.650 --> 39:24.380
beg me to give you an injection.

39:39.730 --> 39:41.300
[Captain Tan]

39:46.360 --> 39:46.990
Chief Tan.

39:47.020 --> 39:48.050
The technicians checked

39:48.050 --> 39:50.010
the security cameras on the ring road

39:50.010 --> 39:51.940
and tracked a black sedan

39:52.010 --> 39:53.370
to the wharf outside the city.

39:53.370 --> 39:55.220
The SWAT team has rushed over there.

39:55.220 --> 39:57.990
While searching the cabins
and containers one by one,

39:57.990 --> 39:59.320
they found that sedan.

39:59.700 --> 40:01.450
The action team is going
to inspect the car now.

40:01.450 --> 40:03.260
I'm calling just to ask you...

40:04.420 --> 40:05.050
Retreat!

40:05.780 --> 40:06.380
What?

40:06.700 --> 40:07.450
It's a trap!

40:07.860 --> 40:08.990
Retreat right away!

40:09.300 --> 40:10.340
Everyone, retreat immediately!

40:10.340 --> 40:11.820
Everyone, retreat immediately!

40:11.820 --> 40:12.420
Retreat!

40:16.050 --> 40:17.450
What's the situation now?

40:17.450 --> 40:18.850
Has everyone pulled out?

40:18.920 --> 40:19.780
Yes, they have.

40:20.570 --> 40:22.740
Qi Yan has
strong anti-detection awareness.

40:22.740 --> 40:23.820
He'll set traps.

40:24.450 --> 40:25.880
From now on, you must be careful

40:25.880 --> 40:26.810
with every move.

40:27.380 --> 40:28.970
Okay, you, too.

40:38.430 --> 40:39.890
We're running out of time.

41:28.700 --> 41:29.260
Speak.

41:32.670 --> 41:33.500
Okay, I got it.

41:35.300 --> 41:36.780
The police suddenly retreated

41:36.780 --> 41:37.910
right before they went in.

41:37.910 --> 41:39.500
Although the car blew up successfully,

41:39.500 --> 41:40.960
none of them were injured.

41:46.780 --> 41:47.710
You may pull out.

41:55.040 --> 41:56.770
They already took my bait

41:58.090 --> 42:00.490
but slipped off the hook
at the last minute.

42:03.620 --> 42:05.350
This must not be a coincidence.

42:06.900 --> 42:07.430
It was...

42:09.110 --> 42:10.370
It was Jiang Hansheng?

42:15.380 --> 42:16.090
Smart.

42:22.570 --> 42:24.530
Here are all the properties
under Wen Hongsheng's name.

42:24.530 --> 42:26.570
He used to be the boss
of Dongsheng Company,

42:26.570 --> 42:28.090
owning 14 properties under his name,

42:28.090 --> 42:30.020
as well as 3 company headquarters.

42:33.220 --> 42:34.550
They don't seem like it.

42:35.570 --> 42:36.090
No.

42:36.700 --> 42:37.570
Nanshan Manor can't be

42:37.570 --> 42:38.970
an ordinary place.

42:39.780 --> 42:40.530
It must mean

42:41.420 --> 42:42.880
something special to him.

42:44.490 --> 42:46.090
Check under Wen Lang's name.

42:46.190 --> 42:46.790
Okay.

43:05.700 --> 43:06.300
Qi Yan.
